### Create a user (Juan - consumer)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account_id": "juan_id",
  "name": "Juan",
  "email": "juan@example.com",
  "profile_picture": "https://example.com/juan.jpg",
  "role": "user",
  "location": "Guadalajara"
}

### Create a provider (Alfredo)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account_id": "alfredo_id",
  "name": "Alfredo",
  "email": "alfredo@example.com",
  "profile_picture": "https://example.com/alfredo.jpg",
  "role": "provider",
  "location": "Guadalajara"
}

### Create a category (Plumbing)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Plumbing",
  "slug": "plumbing",
  "image": "https://example.com/plumbing.jpg",
  "description": "All plumbing related services"
}

### Get all categories
GET http://localhost:3000/api/categories

### Create a review for Alfredo (by Juan)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider_id": "alfredo_id",
  "user_id": "juan_id",
  "rating": 5,
  "title": "Excellent service",
  "comment": "Alfredo was professional and fast"
}

### Create an appointment with Alfredo (by Juan)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider_id": "alfredo_id",
  "user_id": "juan_id",
  "date": "2025-04-10T15:00:00Z"
}

### Get appointments for Alfredo (provider)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/appointments/provider/alfredo_id

### Get appointments for Juan (user)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/appointments/user/juan_id

### Get Alfredo's profile
GET http://localhost:3000/api/providers/alfredo_id
